dct_description_sm: The Public Utilities Commission of the State of Colorado, Denver.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
On verso: Colorado counties, creeks, lakes, mountains and peaks, plateaus, rivers, and towns [list keyed to location on map] -- Colorado electric lines [list keyed to location on map]
